					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Like tepples said, you can overwrite small parts of the name tables with new data, just have the VRAM address point to exact location you want to change before writing the data. There is no need to redraw the whole screen or to patch the background with sprites.
<br />
<br />Just make sure to do all your VRAM updates during VBlank and you should be fine.</div>

