				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">67726e wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">how do I find the VRAM address.</div>
<br />The formula is: NT + (Y * 32) + X
<br />
<br />NT: name table address ($2000, $2400, $2800 or $2C00);
<br />Y: row (0 to 29);
<br />X: column (0 to 31);
<br />
<br />So, to update the tile at coordinates (8, 4) in the first name table you use address: $2000 + (4 * 32) + 8 = $2088.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

