				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you have something in the name table you have obviously written stuff to the PPU before. You have to write the address to $2006 (first the high byte and then the low byte) and the data to $2007.
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;lda #$20<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2006<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;lda #$57<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2006<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;lda #TILE_ID<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;sta $2007</div>
<br />
<br />That's like, the very basics of NES programming. If you are just copying&amp;pasting code and doesn't even know what I'm talking about I guess I can't help you.</div>

